// -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// | TAB  |  Q  |  W  |  E  |  R  |  T  |   |  Y  |  U   |  I  |  O  |  P  | BKSP |
// |Shift |  A  |  S  |  D  |  F  |  G  |   |  H  |  J   |  K  |  L  |  UP | ./>  |
// | Ctrl |  Z  |  X  |  C  |  V  |  B  |   |  N  |  M   | ,/< | LEFT| DOWN| RIGHT|
