   &kp LSHFT &kp N1   &kp N2 &kp N3   &kp N4   &kp N5           &kp N6    &kp N7   &kp N8   &kp N9   &kp N0   &kp EQUAL
   &kp LCTRL &kp N0   &none  &none    &none    &none            &none     &none    &kp LT   &kp GT   &kp FSLH &none
